00030 Dictionary::getMaxID()
00031 {
00032     int s = nsubjects;
00033     int o;
00034     
00035     if (mapping == MAPPING1)
00036         o = nsubjects + nobjects - ssubobj;
00037     else
00038         o = nobjects;
00039         
00040     if (s > o) return s;
00041     else return o;
00042 }
